content: Spent the last few days optimizing Xander's performance with Rust. He's running smoother now, but there's always more to learn. Also, had a romantic evening with Sarah, discussing our future plans. Life's about the journey, not just the destination.

Just got Xander's latest model evaluation results. We're seeing improvements in accuracy and responsiveness. Also, took a break to enjoy a street fair in the East Village. NYC's energy is infectious, fueling my drive to push Xander further.
